channel.title: Imagine Dragons - Believer [Auxy Remake]
channel.description:
OK as I said in the song description, I recently realized that @GOD has already made one of these. I didn't actually know that when I made this, but you should still check out his version (link in description of the song).
If you're confused, I remade **Imagine Dragons - Believer** which is one of the most popular songs recently. Link: https://soundcloud.com/stereofld/believer
Art by me
